hey there

Responses:

Hello, How can I help you? You can say “New Order” or “Track Order”

Good day! What can I do for you today? You can say “New Order” or “Track Order”

Greetings! How can I assist? You can say “New Order” or “Track Order”

Intent: Default Fallback Intent
Response:

I didn’t understand. You can say “New Order” or “Track Order”. Also, in a new order, please mention only items from our available menu: Pizza, Burger, Salad, French fries. Also specify a quantity for each item, for example: “One pizza and 2 fried frees”

Intent: new.order
Training Phrases:

make a new order

create a brand new order

generate a new order

place a new order

new order

Responses:

Ok, starting a new order. You can say things like “I want two pizzas and one fried frees”. Make sure to specify a quantity for every food item! Also, we have only the following items on our menu: Pizza, Burger, Salad, Fried Frees.

Starting new order. Specify food items and quantities. For example, you can say, “I would like to order two pizzas and one fried frees”. Also, we have only the following items on our menu: Pizza, Burger, Salad, Fried Frees.

